<section id="command-hasownpenp">
<title>HASOWNPENP</title>
<indexterm><primary>HASOWNPENP</primary></indexterm>

<variablelist>

<varlistentry><term>Synopsis</term>
<listitem>
<synopsis><command>HASOWNPENP</command>
<command>HASOWNPEN?</command></synopsis>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry><term>Description</term>
<listitem>
<para>
Outputs TRUE if the currently selected turtle has its own setting for <link linkend="command-penmode">PENMODE</link>, <link linkend="command-pensize">PENSIZE</link>, and <link linkend="command-pencolor">PENCOLOR</link>.
Outputs FALSE if the currently selected turtle shares its pen settings with other turtles.
</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry><term>Example</term>
<listitem>

<programlisting><userinput>SETTURTLE 1
SHOW HASOWNPENP</userinput>
false
</programlisting>

<programlisting><userinput>(SETTURTLE 1 "true)
SHOW HASOWNPENP</userinput>
true
</programlisting>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry><term>See Also</term>
<listitem><simplelist>
<member><link linkend="command-setturtle">SETTURTLE</link></member>
</simplelist></listitem>
</varlistentry>

</variablelist>
</section>
